  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a Steam store page description for a game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a pixel art platformer with a lo-fi aesthetic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/5af119a1ea2ee84774587cd968e4f74c.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/5af119a1ea2ee84774587cd968e4f74c.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/5af119a1ea2ee84774587cd968e4f74c.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a nostalgic, Y2K-style scene, playing a pogo-stick game in the rain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the most “pure” funnly, and let it heal your spirit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some players say that this kind of rage game is only played by streamers for their live audiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But my original idea for making this game actually came from a few years ago when I was learning how to swim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I realized that when you’ve just learned to swim, you have to be completely focused.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This state of total concentration—born from the fear of choking and the need to maintain balance—is itself a huge source of fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this noisy era, focus has become a luxury.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/48f3e4caf88a5cac6f008f0624eb25fa.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/48f3e4caf88a5cac6f008f0624eb25fa.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/48f3e4caf88a5cac6f008f0624eb25fa.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game’s controls are simple. Hold down the spacebar when falling, release it when rising.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sounds easy, but I faced the same dilemma as the creator of Getting Over It.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/93a8e3589c24905d0ea2d16266d53557.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/93a8e3589c24905d0ea2d16266d53557.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/93a8e3589c24905d0ea2d16266d53557.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I couldn’t make the controls simple.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learning a new, counterintuitive control scheme is hard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty, the satisfaction, and the level design that comes with it—</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/f6e441d2c82779e4d74f0c2d72fe27c1.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/f6e441d2c82779e4d74f0c2d72fe27c1.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/f6e441d2c82779e4d74f0c2d72fe27c1.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/adba072f6ddb48b85a94df2c87064c64.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/adba072f6ddb48b85a94df2c87064c64.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/adba072f6ddb48b85a94df2c87064c64.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It feels like it already existed somewhere, like it’s part of the rules of the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I just happened to discover it and tried to dig it out in its entirety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay emerged naturally; it wasn’t something I designed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even as the i am creator, now so Skilled with it,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if I don’t play with full focus, I still get utterly destroyed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/d1faba6aa739214db14644c5d6f0ec36.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/d1faba6aa739214db14644c5d6f0ec36.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/d1faba6aa739214db14644c5d6f0ec36.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/20e715a90b653f5dfbffdae341fda09d.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/20e715a90b653f5dfbffdae341fda09d.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/20e715a90b653f5dfbffdae341fda09d.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Games like this often don’t have much replay value after the first playthrough, except for speedrunners.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wanted to change that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To keep the excitement of the first playthrough alive when revisiting the game,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/e743e0b0d94ae22e70e95a163cadda03.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=240 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/e743e0b0d94ae22e70e95a163cadda03.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/e743e0b0d94ae22e70e95a163cadda03.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I added a coin collection mechanic. A fall from too high will make you lose all your coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/1fea3dadd524477c516c6c73c7f2bb26.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/1fea3dadd524477c516c6c73c7f2bb26.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/1fea3dadd524477c516c6c73c7f2bb26.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This means if you want to take your coins all the way to the top to double them, you can’t afford a single major mistake!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/49e7dc719bb1e666a38840ba5292acf6.poster.avif?t=1771770365\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/49e7dc719bb1e666a38840ba5292acf6.webm?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600940/extras/49e7dc719bb1e666a38840ba5292acf6.mp4?t=1771770365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, I’ve upgraded this kind of game. I’ve completed it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s right there now—this gameplay has been realized.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The simple logic of “the higher you jump, the higher you bounce”—</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fantasy that once only existed in my mind has now been brought to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That game is out there now, ready to be played!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
